<paragraph id="F9F66D3F71B6A9D2E9CABC48096A6D30" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">
AFGHANISTAN, 
<emphasis id="C9CC45F6DC3D91E132A3D9BCDA6B5064" italics="true" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">Lindberg</emphasis>
409 (holotype W!).
</paragraph>
