Afghanistan (
<emphasis id="A180EDA782A8AE29FC4D8FEC29203A4A" italics="true" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">Rechinger</emphasis>
35336, 
<emphasis id="644227C47C83F71C9676540CB976FBE0" italics="true" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">Gibbons</emphasis>
